title: it’s fall y’all
itunes:title: it’s fall y’all
description:
IT’S HALLOWEEK and the gals are talking all things fall.  Get excited for a chatty episode with Brooke and Danielle talking about their favorite fall traditions, activities, halloween costumes and so much more.  The gals also share some crazy stories from the past weekend - including a very interesting run in!  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies/stories on Instagram! 


It Happened One Summer Book https://amzn.to/3mgqG0J 
Replica Autumn Vibes Perfume https://bit.ly/3ns3ImV  


Gals On The Go Instagram https://www.instagram.com/galsonthegopodcast/
